title: Software Development
content: Description #F4F5F7 In a sentence or two, Aditya Acharya is a software developer with a robust academic foundation in Electronics and Communication Engineering and a post-graduate degree from the prestigious IIIT Gwalior . With hands-on experience in Node.js , Python , React , and Vue , Aditya builds scalable, efficient, and user-friendly applications. His work bridges the gap between system-level thinking and modern web technologies, making him equally comfortable with backend logic and front-end finesse. describe the purpose of this space.
